WEBVTT

01:40.640 --> 01:45.940
[Speed and Love]

01:46.310 --> 01:48.860
[Episode 20]

01:52.720 --> 01:53.720
Pass me a glass.

01:55.650 --> 01:57.039
Help yourself.

01:58.229 --> 02:00.500
Uncle, everything will be
smooth sailing from now on.

02:00.500 --> 02:02.110
Where we go and how far we go

02:02.290 --> 02:03.170
is all dependent on you

02:03.170 --> 02:04.530
and on Wan's now.

02:04.930 --> 02:05.800
Here, let me toast to you.

02:05.800 --> 02:06.800
Thank you, Uncle.

02:08.710 --> 02:09.840
This is good liquor.

02:11.330 --> 02:12.520
Our champion is back.

02:12.520 --> 02:13.210
Come, have a drink with us.

02:13.210 --> 02:15.120
Come on, pour a drink for our champion!

02:15.120 --> 02:16.320
Our champion is here.

02:17.240 --> 02:17.890
Mr. Wan,

02:19.000 --> 02:20.310
can we chat privately?

02:25.640 --> 02:26.360
Go ahead.

02:27.050 --> 02:28.610
Come, let's keep drinking.

02:32.660 --> 02:33.790
It's about Jin Zhao.

02:35.120 --> 02:36.360
How did he fall?

02:37.170 --> 02:38.570
His skills were lacking.

02:39.079 --> 02:40.340
I could've beaten him.

02:40.730 --> 02:42.050
You've already won.

02:43.170 --> 02:44.829
I could've won on my own merit.

02:47.329 --> 02:48.930
The process doesn't matter.

02:49.250 --> 02:51.640
You are now Wan's Garage's

02:51.700 --> 02:52.660
top driver.

02:54.780 --> 02:55.840
Congratulations.

02:56.360 --> 02:57.420
I don't deserve it.

03:01.520 --> 03:02.450
Now you do.

03:03.820 --> 03:04.890
How ungrateful.

03:06.170 --> 03:07.500
Come on, pour me a drink!

03:07.520 --> 03:08.650
Pour Mr. Wan a drink!

03:08.770 --> 03:10.260
Here we go! Bottom's up!

03:11.310 --> 03:12.790
Fill up all your glasses!

03:13.010 --> 03:14.120
Fill them up!

03:48.329 --> 03:49.590
The call's connected!

04:04.080 --> 04:06.010
If Brandy had his phone on him

04:06.770 --> 04:09.570
and the car exploded,
but the phone still works...

04:10.640 --> 04:11.670
Is it possible that

04:11.670 --> 04:14.000
Brandy wasn't in the car when it exploded?

04:20.550 --> 04:21.870
He wasn't in the car?

04:25.110 --> 04:26.470
Then where could he be?

04:30.610 --> 04:33.010
No news from hospitals or police stations.

04:33.680 --> 04:34.680
Where could he be?

04:41.610 --> 04:42.440
Jiang Mu.

04:46.800 --> 04:48.000
Boss, do you remember

04:48.000 --> 04:50.120
that guy who always wore a baseball cap?

04:50.120 --> 04:51.330
I can't recall.

04:51.360 --> 04:53.880
He often chatted with you,

04:53.900 --> 04:55.320
and he is around my height.

04:55.320 --> 04:56.610
You mean Lu,

04:56.680 --> 04:57.650
who often buys from me?

04:57.650 --> 04:59.240
Yes, do you have his contact info?

04:59.240 --> 05:00.020
Could I get his phone number?

05:00.020 --> 05:00.900
Just a moment.

05:01.210 --> 05:05.090
0264530204.

05:05.120 --> 05:05.780
That's correct.

05:05.780 --> 05:06.450
Thank you, Boss.

05:06.450 --> 05:07.250
No problem.

05:08.290 --> 05:09.050
I got it!

05:09.410 --> 05:10.120
Here.

05:32.870 --> 05:33.940
Hello, Officer Lu.

05:34.720 --> 05:35.680
This is Jiang Mu.

05:38.550 --> 05:39.550
Jin Zhao, is he...

05:42.260 --> 05:43.350
Is he still alive?

05:47.040 --> 05:47.970
Give me a moment.

05:51.170 --> 05:51.810
Fu.

05:52.220 --> 05:53.420
Keep an eye on things.

05:58.180 --> 05:59.110
Jiang Mu, right?

06:02.530 --> 06:03.630
Jin Zhao is still in critical condition.

06:03.630 --> 06:05.760
I'll let you know when I have good news.

06:17.020 --> 06:17.690
Okay.

06:21.180 --> 06:22.820
Can I at least visit him?

06:23.240 --> 06:23.920
No.

06:25.020 --> 06:29.840
♪ Forgotten between the rearview mirror ♪

06:25.980 --> 06:27.730
It's just that...

06:28.390 --> 06:30.250
I can't tell you where he currently is.

06:30.250 --> 06:31.910
Do you understand what I mean?

06:32.170 --> 06:37.550
♪ Seeing your long unseen face
on that rainy night ♪

06:36.320 --> 06:37.090
I'm sorry.

06:37.650 --> 06:39.360
The situation is somewhat sensitive,

06:39.360 --> 06:40.240
so it's not possible right now.

06:39.880 --> 06:45.360
♪ Counting backwards to
the unfulfilled promises ♪

06:46.890 --> 06:52.550
♪ The heart that is still beating
hasn't said goodbye yet ♪

06:53.480 --> 06:56.330
♪ Meeting again after many years ♪

06:56.820 --> 06:59.730
♪ The coffee is too sour and bitter;
I'm greedy for something sweet ♪

07:00.870 --> 07:03.500
♪ Who will circle around the line
bordering the thoughts? ♪

07:03.860 --> 07:07.990
♪ Stupidly,
I refuse to believe there's an end ♪

07:08.760 --> 07:10.750
♪ I must ♪

07:10.770 --> 07:14.590
♪ Continue to love,
between the sun and the moon ♪

07:14.610 --> 07:18.020
♪ Even in pain,
we indulge in the iron-like vows ♪

07:18.230 --> 07:19.750
♪ Willingly ♪

07:22.370 --> 07:25.590
♪ At this moment ♪

07:25.810 --> 07:29.250
♪ I run towards you
before the night falls ♪

07:29.270 --> 07:33.790
♪ Don't ask about the past;
just bet on tomorrow ♪

07:33.830 --> 07:37.000
♪ Those dreams and longings ♪

07:38.310 --> 07:40.300
♪ I must ♪

07:40.930 --> 07:44.110
♪ Continue to love,
between the sun and the moon ♪

07:44.300 --> 07:47.710
♪ Even in pain,
we indulge in the iron-like vows ♪

07:47.860 --> 07:49.380
♪ Willingly ♪

07:52.060 --> 07:55.280
♪ At this moment ♪

07:55.500 --> 07:58.940
♪ I run towards you
before the night falls ♪

07:58.960 --> 08:03.480
♪ Don't ask about the past;
just bet on tomorrow ♪

08:03.500 --> 08:06.670
♪ Those dreams and longings ♪

08:06.930 --> 08:11.200
♪ The trails overlap again ♪

08:30.680 --> 08:31.730
Why is it you?

08:51.010 --> 08:52.160
Why are you here?

08:53.390 --> 08:54.250
Where's my mom?

08:57.110 --> 08:58.350
Yinghan didn't come.

08:59.900 --> 09:00.590
Mu.

09:01.860 --> 09:03.460
I have something to tell you.

09:04.950 --> 09:07.230
You may not be able to accept it just yet,

09:07.630 --> 09:09.320
but I think I must tell you.

09:12.720 --> 09:13.720
Around...

09:14.200 --> 09:15.410
last October,

09:16.820 --> 09:19.350
five and a half months after
I met your mother,

09:19.830 --> 09:21.560
your mother was diagnosed with

09:22.560 --> 09:23.890
aortic stenosis,

09:24.350 --> 09:26.010
with a severity of 78 percent.

09:26.770 --> 09:28.840
The diagnosis is aortic stenosis,

09:29.010 --> 09:30.770
with a severity of 78 percent.

09:31.170 --> 09:32.700
You need surgery urgently.

09:34.290 --> 09:34.840
This...

09:35.080 --> 09:36.940
Doctor, what exactly do you mean?

09:37.680 --> 09:38.840
Aortic stenosis

09:38.960 --> 09:41.560
becomes very serious when it
exceeds 75 percent.

09:41.560 --> 09:43.010
If it progresses further,

09:43.010 --> 09:45.340
the blood vessels could become
completely blocked.

09:45.340 --> 09:48.010
We need to perform
the coronary bypass surgery

09:48.220 --> 09:50.220
to establish a new pathway.

09:54.370 --> 09:55.700
You can think it over,

09:56.410 --> 09:57.940
but please decide quickly.

10:15.720 --> 10:16.780
Thank you, Doctor.

10:32.960 --> 10:33.770
Chris.

10:35.260 --> 10:36.420
Let's break up.

10:36.900 --> 10:37.620
What?

10:39.120 --> 10:40.920
You know about my condition now.

10:41.280 --> 10:43.120
I don't want to become your burden.

10:43.120 --> 10:44.130
This is just an illness.

10:44.130 --> 10:45.530
Why should we break up?

10:45.860 --> 10:48.270
The doctor said I need surgery,

10:48.790 --> 10:49.720
and this surgery

10:49.810 --> 10:51.500
isn't 100 percent guaranteed to succeed.

10:51.500 --> 10:52.900
Even if it's successful,

10:53.670 --> 10:55.930
full recovery isn't guaranteed either.

10:56.740 --> 10:58.210
I don't want to be a burden to you.

10:58.210 --> 10:59.330
So what?

11:00.440 --> 11:02.010
We are 100 percent in love.

11:02.090 --> 11:03.490
That's all that matters.

11:04.650 --> 11:06.980
Why do you have to be
so brutal to yourself?

11:08.370 --> 11:09.170
We're lovers?

11:11.370 --> 11:12.180
Yes.

11:14.800 --> 11:15.680
Darling,

11:17.000 --> 11:18.120
let's get married.

11:25.830 --> 11:26.790
Marry me.

11:31.410 --> 11:33.300
Are you proposing to me now?

11:36.580 --> 11:37.790
I have a good friend

11:38.160 --> 11:39.200
in Canada

11:39.560 --> 11:40.960
who's a cardiovascular specialist.

11:40.960 --> 11:41.890
When we get back,

11:42.310 --> 11:43.780
I'll email him right away.

11:43.990 --> 11:44.900
If possible,

11:45.310 --> 11:47.240
we'll go to Canada for the surgery.

11:49.320 --> 11:50.320
I'll do as you say.

11:52.320 --> 11:54.290
Also, we should tell Mumu.

11:54.720 --> 11:55.330
No.

11:56.440 --> 11:57.800
We can't tell Mumu.

11:58.230 --> 12:00.160
But I think having Mumu by your side

12:00.360 --> 12:02.090
would help you recover faster.

12:02.400 --> 12:03.050
No.

12:03.770 --> 12:05.570
We absolutely cannot tell Mumu.

12:05.890 --> 12:07.130
She's still a child.

12:07.960 --> 12:09.360
I don't want to burden her

12:09.680 --> 12:10.960
or make her worry.

12:11.330 --> 12:12.570
So you must promise me

12:12.880 --> 12:14.430
to keep this from Mumu.

12:15.250 --> 12:15.960
Otherwise,

12:16.370 --> 12:17.410
I won't get treatment.

12:17.410 --> 12:18.060
You...

12:21.360 --> 12:22.120
Alright.

12:23.660 --> 12:24.720
I'll do as you wish.

12:37.570 --> 12:39.090
Just recently,

12:40.010 --> 12:42.650
your mom's surgery went smoothly.

12:45.080 --> 12:47.210
I just hope you can accompany her to her

12:47.930 --> 12:49.390
follow-up appointments.

12:49.880 --> 12:51.750
Since your mom got sick,

12:52.290 --> 12:54.150
she keeps looking at your photos.

12:55.210 --> 12:56.810
I know she really misses you.

13:04.540 --> 13:05.680
Mu.

13:09.680 --> 13:11.800
Your mom really needs you now.

13:24.050 --> 13:24.890
I'm sorry,

13:25.530 --> 13:26.410
Chris,

13:27.840 --> 13:30.100
for my attitude towards you previously.

13:30.680 --> 13:33.280
Thank you for staying with
my mom all this time.

13:33.480 --> 13:34.410
Mu,

13:35.930 --> 13:37.200
we are family.

13:49.080 --> 13:50.810
I'll go back to Canada with you.

14:05.800 --> 14:06.680
Zhao.

14:07.650 --> 14:10.180
My stepfather came to look for me
from Canada.

14:10.480 --> 14:11.470
He told me

14:11.550 --> 14:14.660
♪ I leave after your curtain call ♪

14:12.410 --> 14:14.480
my mom just had a heart surgery.

14:15.130 --> 14:17.410
She's not doing well after the surgery.

14:17.360 --> 14:20.560
♪ I ask the tired bird ♪

14:19.290 --> 14:20.290
My mom...

14:21.350 --> 14:24.400
♪ About your news ♪

14:21.560 --> 14:23.080
needs me too.

14:25.010 --> 14:26.890
I must go back to Canada.

14:26.670 --> 14:30.320
♪ You're too serious in
both your passion and silence ♪

14:28.010 --> 14:28.840
After that,

14:29.410 --> 14:31.320
I might stay with her afterwards

14:31.320 --> 14:32.520
and keep her company.

14:32.630 --> 14:37.820
♪ That's why you're always
covered in scars ♪

14:34.770 --> 14:35.800
I'm sorry,

14:36.560 --> 14:37.440
Zhao.

14:39.330 --> 14:42.930
♪ If darkness can stop the pain ♪

14:43.200 --> 14:48.390
♪ I'll let you sleep a bit longer ♪

14:49.950 --> 14:53.960
♪ I'll stay by your side tonight ♪

14:56.810 --> 15:01.920
♪ I want to meet the dusk with you ♪

15:02.270 --> 15:06.150
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

15:06.920 --> 15:12.960
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

15:13.710 --> 15:17.360
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

15:17.530 --> 15:21.640
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

15:22.110 --> 15:25.900
♪ But I'm still waiting
for every dawn and dusk ♪

15:25.930 --> 15:29.860
♪ To run towards you again ♪

15:30.890 --> 15:37.740
♪ Even if I hug you for a moment ♪

15:54.340 --> 15:59.070
♪ Perhaps the tides have carried
all the echoes away ♪

16:00.830 --> 16:06.220
♪ How could you not hear me at all? ♪

16:07.260 --> 16:11.270
♪ Every time I see you ♪

16:11.440 --> 16:16.140
♪ You take a part of my soul ♪

16:13.930 --> 16:16.050
If Zhao doesn't reply soon,

16:16.890 --> 16:18.440
there won't be any time left.

16:17.930 --> 16:21.890
♪ And longing slips in ♪

16:22.140 --> 16:26.380
♪ I want to meet the dusk with you ♪

16:22.460 --> 16:23.250
Zhao,

16:24.160 --> 16:25.440
I am leaving soon.

16:26.450 --> 16:30.220
♪ Then stay with me until dawn ♪

16:26.840 --> 16:28.250
If you see this,

16:28.590 --> 16:30.720
please contact me as soon as possible.

16:30.860 --> 16:35.940
♪ Our moment together
feels like a lifetime ♪

16:31.840 --> 16:33.290
Missing you, Mu.

16:37.570 --> 16:41.210
♪ Your remaining warmth before dawn ♪

16:41.320 --> 16:45.710
♪ Is enough for me to sink in soberly ♪

16:45.780 --> 16:47.780
♪ But I'm still waiting ♪

16:48.060 --> 16:49.710
♪ For every dawn and dusk ♪

16:49.730 --> 16:53.660
♪ To run towards you again ♪

16:53.960 --> 16:57.630
♪ Until I can embrace you ♪

16:58.220 --> 17:00.220
♪ Can you hear me ♪

17:00.250 --> 17:02.060
♪ Your heart also aches, right? ♪

17:02.090 --> 17:05.800
♪ Those days and nights were not a waste ♪

17:05.819 --> 17:11.740
♪ How long will it take to answer ♪

17:24.780 --> 17:25.500
Jin Zhao.

17:27.410 --> 17:28.410
Officer Lu.

17:31.870 --> 17:33.130
You're finally awake.

17:36.760 --> 17:37.600
Don't move.

17:38.720 --> 17:40.520
You've been seriously injured.

17:40.850 --> 17:43.110
You've been unconscious for a long time.

17:50.960 --> 17:53.160
Jiang Mu has been trying to contact you,

17:53.770 --> 17:55.900
but I didn't know how to respond to her.

18:40.870 --> 18:41.620
Don't move.

18:47.070 --> 18:47.950
Find Sanlai.

18:48.810 --> 18:49.570
Find...

18:50.520 --> 18:51.850
Help me contact Sanlai.

18:54.020 --> 18:55.460
Okay, I'll contact him.

18:56.730 --> 18:58.590
Stay still. I'll call the doctor.

19:43.930 --> 19:45.460
I'll have Sanlai pick you up

19:45.610 --> 19:46.960
tomorrow morning.

19:47.770 --> 19:48.570
Let's meet.

20:14.240 --> 20:15.240
Brandy is inside.

20:28.650 --> 20:31.510
You've been in touch with him
for a while now, right?

20:34.010 --> 20:35.360
Why didn't you tell me?

20:39.300 --> 20:40.430
Brandy is upstairs.

20:43.110 --> 20:44.240
Go ask him yourself.

22:41.990 --> 22:45.540
[Vancouver]

22:54.200 --> 22:54.960
Mom.

22:58.200 --> 22:59.930
My Mu has finally returned.

23:01.800 --> 23:03.260
You've finally returned.

23:05.000 --> 23:06.530
It's great to have you back.

23:06.650 --> 23:08.180
It's great to have you back.

23:11.060 --> 23:11.820
Mom.

23:13.510 --> 23:14.270
I'm sorry.

23:14.480 --> 23:16.140
I didn't know you were so sick.

23:16.240 --> 23:17.330
If I had known,

23:17.350 --> 23:18.850
I wouldn't have been so wilful.

23:18.850 --> 23:19.930
Silly child.

23:20.530 --> 23:22.990
Aren't I standing right here
in front of you?

23:24.440 --> 23:25.410
The doctor said

23:25.650 --> 23:26.850
as long as I keep up with

23:26.850 --> 23:29.510
regular follow-up appointments,
I'll be fine.

23:30.770 --> 23:31.600
From now on,

23:32.400 --> 23:34.730
I'll accompany you to your appointments.

23:35.810 --> 23:37.920
I'll listen to my precious daughter
from now on.

23:37.920 --> 23:38.920
Whatever you say.

23:41.280 --> 23:42.740
Don't cry, my silly child.

23:44.610 --> 23:45.680
It's time to eat!

23:47.440 --> 23:48.240
Come inside.

23:48.340 --> 23:49.620
Let's eat.

23:52.130 --> 23:53.000
Are you tired?

24:01.170 --> 24:03.240
Please pay attention to the
Hertzsprung-Russell diagram on the screen.

24:03.240 --> 24:03.930
These in the upper left corner,

24:03.930 --> 24:04.670
the O-type main sequence stars
have surface temperatures

24:04.670 --> 24:05.850
that can reach 30,000 Kelvin.

24:05.850 --> 24:06.720
Just imagine.

24:08.050 --> 24:09.330
This is three orders of magnitude hotter

24:09.330 --> 24:10.960
than the plasma we can generate
in our laboratory.

24:10.960 --> 24:12.610
The Crab Nebula you see now

24:13.170 --> 24:15.300
is actually the remnant of a supernova

24:18.720 --> 24:20.120
that exploded in 1054 AD.

24:22.320 --> 24:23.580
Its central pulsar has

24:23.780 --> 24:25.850
a rotation period of 33 milliseconds,

24:25.850 --> 24:27.960
like the most precise atomic clock
in the universe.

24:27.960 --> 24:29.640
I'm studying natural science,

24:29.640 --> 24:31.640
focusing on physics and astronomy.

24:32.040 --> 24:34.650
Currently, my studies are
really challenging to me.

24:34.650 --> 24:37.240
I barely understand
any of the technical terms

24:37.240 --> 24:38.840
our professors use in class.

24:38.890 --> 24:40.520
Sometimes after a lecture,

24:40.840 --> 24:43.110
it feels like
I've been listening to gibberish.

24:43.110 --> 24:44.840
The pressure is overwhelming.

24:45.350 --> 24:48.760
I wish you were here with me.

24:51.570 --> 24:53.200
The coffee here is so bitter,

24:53.810 --> 24:54.960
it's awful.

24:55.890 --> 24:56.760
You know,

24:56.930 --> 24:59.280
I go home every month on weekends

24:59.610 --> 25:01.650
to stay with Mom at Chris' house.

25:01.810 --> 25:04.200
Her condition is gradually improving.

25:04.740 --> 25:05.860
I often tell her

25:05.890 --> 25:07.930
about our time together in Manshi.

25:08.260 --> 25:09.300
Sometimes,

25:09.610 --> 25:12.280
she even takes the initiative
to ask me about you.

25:12.280 --> 25:15.100
But I don't know the exact situation
on your end either,

25:15.100 --> 25:16.340
so I can only tell Mom

25:16.460 --> 25:17.790
that you're doing fine.

25:19.020 --> 25:19.890
But...

25:20.720 --> 25:21.930
are you really okay?

25:23.110 --> 25:25.110
Once things are settled on your end,

25:25.270 --> 25:26.930
you'll come see me, won't you?

25:34.360 --> 25:36.200
From your voice, you seem like...

25:36.200 --> 25:37.800
you're still not doing well.

25:40.400 --> 25:41.730
I'm still alive for now.

25:41.810 --> 25:43.410
I'd like to recommend someone to you.

25:43.410 --> 25:44.330
Dr. Julia.

25:44.590 --> 25:46.040
She's a good friend of mine

25:46.040 --> 25:48.370
and an excellent rehabilitation doctor.

25:49.150 --> 25:50.430
She'll definitely be of help to you.

25:50.430 --> 25:51.560
She'll be here soon.

26:05.520 --> 26:06.190
Hello,

26:06.720 --> 26:07.650
I'm Julia.

26:08.130 --> 26:10.090
Lin Sui should have told you about me.

26:10.090 --> 26:12.310
He specifically invited me back
from Canada.

26:12.310 --> 26:14.710
The upcoming rehabilitation
will be very tough,

26:14.710 --> 26:15.630
but believe me,

26:16.030 --> 26:17.630
it will definitely help you.

26:25.080 --> 26:25.880
Hold it there.

26:30.570 --> 26:32.100
Try to control it yourself.

26:33.240 --> 26:34.240
Relax.

26:36.100 --> 26:37.170
Don't fight me.

26:37.960 --> 26:38.600
Yes.

26:38.860 --> 26:40.260
Push harder. Control it.

26:43.650 --> 26:44.480
Great!

26:44.930 --> 26:46.170
In the early stages, we'll work through

26:46.170 --> 26:47.900
hip and knee flexion exercises

26:48.000 --> 26:50.610
to train your joint mobility and strength.

26:52.070 --> 26:53.350
Now, try it yourself.

26:53.610 --> 26:54.410
Bend.

27:18.600 --> 27:19.250
Zhao,

27:19.410 --> 27:21.650
I've gradually adapted to life here

27:21.850 --> 27:23.090
and made new friends.

27:23.510 --> 27:24.220
Also,

27:24.420 --> 27:25.730
all those difficult technical terms

27:25.730 --> 27:27.580
our professors use in class,

27:27.740 --> 27:29.400
I can understand them all now.

27:29.930 --> 27:30.650
Zhao,

27:31.060 --> 27:32.520
how are things over there?

27:33.330 --> 27:34.440
In terms of surgery,

27:34.440 --> 27:36.240
we've done all we can.

27:36.410 --> 27:39.090
The rest depends mainly on rehabilitation.

27:39.290 --> 27:40.090
I understand.

27:41.480 --> 27:42.280
Doctor,

27:44.810 --> 27:46.410
will he be able to race again?

27:46.610 --> 27:47.520
Racing?

27:48.170 --> 27:49.190
Being able to stand

27:49.190 --> 27:51.440
and live without a wheelchair
would be fortunate enough.

27:51.440 --> 27:52.640
Forget about racing.

27:53.240 --> 27:53.890
Sir,

27:54.060 --> 27:56.120
your spinal nerves have been injured

27:56.340 --> 27:58.340
and you have multiple tendon tears.

27:58.370 --> 27:59.440
The rehabilitation process

27:59.440 --> 28:00.700
will be extremely long and painful.

28:00.700 --> 28:02.430
You must be mentally prepared.

28:05.170 --> 28:06.040
Thank you.

28:06.240 --> 28:07.240
Let me see you out.

28:08.620 --> 28:10.510
Contact me if you need anything.

28:31.280 --> 28:32.810
Jiang Mu sent you a message?

28:35.030 --> 28:38.760
She's been messaging you a lot
these past three months, hasn't she?

28:41.660 --> 28:44.390
You didn't leave all of them unanswered,
did you?

28:45.440 --> 28:46.840
In my current condition,

28:48.600 --> 28:50.530
how am I supposed to respond to her?

28:52.480 --> 28:53.890
Should I tell her,

28:57.300 --> 28:58.130
"Mu,

29:00.070 --> 29:02.470
I'll most likely be disabled
in the future,

29:05.250 --> 29:06.510
either using crutches

29:07.280 --> 29:08.340
or in a wheelchair.

29:10.210 --> 29:12.140
Would you still want to be with me?"

29:14.330 --> 29:15.480
Jiang Mu would be willing.

29:15.480 --> 29:16.480
But I'm not.

29:22.130 --> 29:24.200
She deserves a better life.

29:27.330 --> 29:29.330
Besides, the case isn't closed yet.

29:32.980 --> 29:33.740
Sanlai,

29:35.940 --> 29:37.400
don't contact her either.

29:40.080 --> 29:40.910
We...

29:50.300 --> 29:51.460
We should all try

29:53.960 --> 29:55.610
to give her a peaceful life.

31:11.160 --> 31:12.440
I'm right here.

31:12.680 --> 31:15.080
You don't need
to be yearning day and night.

31:17.370 --> 31:18.630
I want to clear my name.

31:19.680 --> 31:21.210
Especially after you came.

31:22.710 --> 31:24.080
I want this proof of innocence even more.

31:23.010 --> 31:29.410
♪ Perhaps the weather's damp and mild ♪

31:25.520 --> 31:26.890
I want to prove myself.

31:28.790 --> 31:29.590
At the very least,

31:29.430 --> 31:33.260
♪ Perhaps it's about the habit
of bearing ♪

31:30.630 --> 31:31.670
I deserve you.

31:33.970 --> 31:37.260
♪ A certain bitter emotion ♪

31:37.280 --> 31:43.350
♪ For you, it's all too easy ♪

31:41.890 --> 31:42.890
All my life,

31:43.680 --> 31:45.480
people have come and gone.

31:44.300 --> 31:50.010
♪ To be happy or heartbroken,
as transparent as I can be ♪

31:46.720 --> 31:48.850
I've never been serious about anyone.

31:50.610 --> 31:52.340
So once I get serious,

31:51.000 --> 31:56.910
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 10,000 kilometers ♪

31:55.200 --> 31:58.200
I probably won't give you
a chance to change your mind.

31:58.250 --> 32:04.410
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

31:59.280 --> 32:00.600
I won't change my mind.

32:04.560 --> 32:05.720
♪ I believe ♪

32:05.740 --> 32:09.910
♪ Maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

32:10.170 --> 32:13.400
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

32:13.980 --> 32:19.010
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

32:14.370 --> 32:15.330
Zhao.

32:16.160 --> 32:18.490
Why won't you reply to my messages?

32:19.070 --> 32:20.230
Even if you simply reply,

32:19.850 --> 32:25.760
♪ Crossing the line for love,
I've walked 10,000 kilometers ♪

32:20.850 --> 32:21.760
"I got it."

32:22.280 --> 32:24.710
Even just an emoji would be fine.

32:25.890 --> 32:28.570
Why won't you respond to me?

32:27.110 --> 32:33.250
♪ Brave enough to be sure is my instinct ♪

32:33.280 --> 32:38.390
♪ I believe
maybe it just takes a little resolve ♪

32:38.660 --> 32:42.000
♪ To turn wishes into shooting stars ♪

32:42.430 --> 32:47.200
♪ Mirroring the eyes that gaze at me ♪

32:53.180 --> 33:00.070
♪ Crossing the path,
stepping into your life ♪

33:08.340 --> 33:09.670
Are you feeling better?

33:13.370 --> 33:15.230
This sort of pain will come again.

33:15.890 --> 33:17.150
Some of it is physical.

33:17.260 --> 33:19.680
Some of it are triggered by
traumatic memories.

33:19.680 --> 33:21.040
But mostly,

33:21.200 --> 33:23.440
it's psychological and
physical pain intertwined.

33:23.440 --> 33:24.170
So,

33:25.000 --> 33:25.850
don't worry.

33:26.090 --> 33:27.000
I'll help you.

33:30.240 --> 33:30.960
Just relax.

33:31.240 --> 33:32.240
I'll go get busy now.

33:32.240 --> 33:33.840
Call me if you need anything.

33:38.790 --> 33:40.720
Lift your feet up. Don't drag them.

33:43.180 --> 33:44.580
Each step can be smaller,

33:45.020 --> 33:46.220
but keep them steady.

33:50.810 --> 33:51.730
Relax your upper body.

33:51.730 --> 33:54.260
Try to use the strength
from your lower limbs.

34:00.070 --> 34:01.310
Good. Go slower.

34:04.520 --> 34:05.150
Yes.

34:06.390 --> 34:07.280
Lift your foot.

34:14.570 --> 34:15.340
Very good.

34:20.179 --> 34:20.820
Good.

34:26.880 --> 34:27.810
Talented people

34:27.860 --> 34:29.860
tend to bounce back pretty quickly.

34:32.730 --> 34:34.190
Let's stop here for today.

34:36.480 --> 34:37.120
Thank you.

34:40.440 --> 34:41.370
Have some water.

34:49.080 --> 34:50.409
I have good news for you.

34:52.080 --> 34:53.480
The case has been solved.

34:57.560 --> 34:58.250
Really?

34:59.080 --> 35:00.940
The amount involved is enormous.

35:01.040 --> 35:02.770
Approaching 800 million yuan.

35:03.690 --> 35:06.410
It was largely thanks to He Zhang
turning himself in

35:06.410 --> 35:07.770
and becoming a prosecution witness

35:07.770 --> 35:09.970
that the case had a major breakthrough.

35:18.770 --> 35:19.970
What brings you here?

35:20.640 --> 35:21.410
I'm sorry.

35:30.640 --> 35:32.300
Why are you apologizing to me?

35:34.040 --> 35:34.960
Because...

35:38.520 --> 35:39.980
I don't want to lose to you.

35:47.430 --> 35:48.800
When I was at Wan's,

35:50.140 --> 35:52.070
I did many things that wronged you.

35:54.070 --> 35:56.800
But about Wan Shengbang
tampering with your car,

35:57.760 --> 35:58.890
I truly didn't know.

36:03.930 --> 36:04.660
Jin Zhao,

36:07.850 --> 36:09.310
if there's still a chance,

36:11.750 --> 36:14.010
I wish to challenge you fairly once more.

36:23.980 --> 36:25.510
I'm going to turn myself in.

36:36.290 --> 36:37.430
He Zhang provided information

36:37.430 --> 36:40.490
on the trading methods between
Wan's and the Alliance.

36:44.750 --> 36:47.370
The Navy Headquarters and
the Anti-Smuggling Bureau joined forces,

36:47.370 --> 36:49.810
and with police departments
cooperating nationwide,

36:49.810 --> 36:51.810
we've arrested everyone involved.

36:52.690 --> 36:54.730
Wan Dayong was caught immediately.

36:55.370 --> 36:56.570
As for Wan Shengbang,

36:56.690 --> 36:58.890
he was caught while fleeing to Vietnam.

36:59.160 --> 37:00.770
As for your accident,

37:01.210 --> 37:03.330
Wan Shengbang coerced your mechanic

37:03.560 --> 37:05.000
by threatening his family's safety,

37:05.000 --> 37:06.880
forcing him to tamper with your car's

37:06.880 --> 37:07.810
braking system,

37:08.210 --> 37:09.740
which caused the accident.

37:09.930 --> 37:11.660
The mechanic has been arrested

37:12.000 --> 37:13.800
and awaits further processing.

37:15.810 --> 37:16.480
In short,

37:16.850 --> 37:18.000
no one got away.

37:21.250 --> 37:22.650
That puts my mind at ease.

37:23.600 --> 37:25.160
During the first interrogation,

37:25.160 --> 37:27.090
Wan Dayong confessed everything,

37:28.370 --> 37:30.600
including your case from years ago.

37:32.080 --> 37:33.540
The guy honestly admitted

37:34.440 --> 37:35.640
that he swapped out parts

37:35.640 --> 37:37.370
using inferior replacements.

37:37.560 --> 37:39.160
You had nothing to do with it.

37:46.880 --> 37:47.730
Thank you.

37:48.890 --> 37:50.420
My wish has been fulfilled.

37:54.560 --> 37:55.410
Jin Zhao,

37:56.320 --> 37:57.780
we should be thanking you.

38:00.480 --> 38:02.610
You've been through a lot these years.

38:07.670 --> 38:09.120
Alright, I have work to do.

38:09.120 --> 38:10.650
Take good care of yourself.

38:39.470 --> 38:40.370
I saw the news.

38:40.400 --> 38:41.610
Is it all over now?

39:57.470 --> 39:58.600
During this time...

40:01.750 --> 40:03.230
you must have been so worried.

40:03.230 --> 40:04.500
Is the mission over?

40:08.540 --> 40:09.260
Almost.

40:11.400 --> 40:12.830
Did you see the Luminous Pearl

40:12.830 --> 40:13.950
from that night?

40:19.940 --> 40:20.750
Yes, I did.

40:22.410 --> 40:23.100
So...

40:23.670 --> 40:24.710
when the explosion happened,

40:24.710 --> 40:25.590
you weren't there.
